text: Zoulehia Abzetta Dabonne (born 15 December 1992) is an Ivory Coast judoka. At the 2016 Summer Olympics she competed in the Women's -57 kg. ==References== Category:Olympic judoka of Ivory Coast Category:1992 births Category:Judoka at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Living people Category:Ivorian female judoka Category:African Games silver medalists for Ivory Coast Category:African Games medalists in judo Category:Competitors at the 2015 African Games
